        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Optimize by adjusting batch sizes, enabling caching for frequent queries, and scaling horizontally based on load patterns. Monitor these metrics continuously using tools like Prometheus or Grafana."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "h2",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "4. Production Deployment Strategies"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Deploy Chatterbox in containerized environments with orchestration tools like Kubernetes for auto-scaling. Implement health checks and circuit breakers to maintain system stability. Use canary releases to test updates gradually, minimizing downtime. Ensure logging and tracing are in place for debugging, and regularly review benchmark data to adapt to changing traffic demands."
          }
        ]
